---containers---
https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.6/layout/overview/#containers

container : gives some spage around teh element
 <div class="container bg-primary">
                CONTAINER FIELD
</div>
---------------
cotainer-fluid : does not give any spage around the element
gives full width
<div class="container-fluid bg-success">
    CONTAINER FLUID FIELD
</div>


